                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-lg-3 text-end d-lg-flex align-items-start">
                                        <div class="sold-out text-start">
                                            <span class="fw-bold lh-base text-lg-center">商品已售罄</span>
                                            <span class="mt-2 text-lg-start d-block text-start ">請重新選擇商品</span>
